column2: SELECT   specObjID,   d4#,	    -- #AA break, Bruzual (#) definition   d4#_err,        -- Uncertainty estimate for #AA break, Bruzual (#) definition   d4#_model,      -- #AA break, Bruzual (#) definition measured off best-fit CB0# model   d4#_sub,	    -- #AA break, Bruzual (#) definition after correction for emission lines   d4#_sub_err,    -- Uncertainty estimate for #AA break, Bruzual (#) definition after correction for emission lines   d4#_n,          -- #AA break, Balogh et al (#) definition   d4#_n_err,	    -- Uncertainty estimate for #AA break, Balogh et al (#) definition   d4#_n_model,    -- #AA break, Balogh et al (#) definition measured off best-fit CB0# model   d4#_n_sub,	    -- #AA break, Balogh et al (#) definition after correction for emission lines   d4#_n_sub_err,  -- Uncertainty estimate for #AA break, Balogh et al (#) definition after correction for emission lines   d4#_red,	    -- The flux in the red window of the Bruzual (#) definition of D4#   d4#_blue,	    -- The flux in the blue window of the Bruzual (#) definition of D4#   d4#_n_red,	    -- The flux in the red window of the Balogh et al (#) definition of D4#   d4#_n_blue,	    -- The flux in the blue window of the Balogh et al (#) definition of D4#   d4#_sub_red,    -- The flux in the red window of the Bruzual (#) definition of D4# after subtraction of emission lines   d4#_sub_blue,   -- The flux in the blue window of the Bruzual (#) definition of D4# after subtraction of emission lines   d4#_n_sub_red,  -- The flux in the red window of the Balogh et al (#) definition of D4# after subtraction of emission lines   d4#_n_sub_blue, -- The flux in the blue window of the Balogh et al (#)q definition of D4# after subtraction of emission lines     FROM dr1#.galSpecIndx -- Index measurements of spectra from the MPA-JHU spectroscopic catalogue.
